<body>
    <h1>Developer Induction Questions</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h4 id=3D"DeveloperInductionQuestions-Question1">Question 1</h4>
<p>Which of these is NOT a responsibility of a Mesh Developer?</p>
<ul>
<li>Perform deployments to the platform</li>
<li>Ensure that secure coding practices are followed</li>
<li>Propose new components</li>
<li>Write unit tests, idempotent tests and contract tests</li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<div id=3D"expander-696451330" class=3D"expand-container">
<div role=3D"heading" aria-level=3D"6" id=3D"expander-control-696451330" cl=
ass=3D"expand-control"><button type=3D"button" id=3D"expand-button-69645133=
0" class=3D"aui-button aui-button-link aui-button-link-icon-text" aria-expa=
nded=3D"true" aria-controls=3D"expander-content-696451330"><span class=3D"e=
xpand-icon aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-chevron-down" aria-hidden=
=3D"true"></span><span class=3D"expand-control-text conf-macro-render">Clic=
k here to expand...</span></button>
</div>
<div role=3D"region" id=3D"expander-content-696451330" class=3D"expand-cont=
ent" aria-labelledby=3D"expand-button-696451330">
<p><strong>Propose new components</strong></p>
<p>Proposing new components is the resposibility of the Domain Architect.</=
p>
</div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<h4 id=3D"DeveloperInductionQuestions-Question2">Question 2</h4>
<p>Which of these commands allows you to create a temporary component, for =
experimenting on the Mesh platform?</p>
<ul>
<li><code>mesh sandbox</code></li>
<li><code>mesh incubate</code></li>
<li><code>mesh build</code></li>
<li><code>mesh create component</code></li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<div id=3D"expander-470846280" class=3D"expand-container">
<div role=3D"heading" aria-level=3D"6" id=3D"expander-control-470846280" cl=
ass=3D"expand-control"><button type=3D"button" id=3D"expand-button-47084628=
0" class=3D"aui-button aui-button-link aui-button-link-icon-text" aria-expa=
nded=3D"true" aria-controls=3D"expander-content-470846280"><span class=3D"e=
xpand-icon aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-chevron-down" aria-hidden=
=3D"true"></span><span class=3D"expand-control-text conf-macro-render">Clic=
k here to expand...</span></button>
</div>
<div role=3D"region" id=3D"expander-content-470846280" class=3D"expand-cont=
ent" aria-labelledby=3D"expand-button-470846280">
<p><strong><code>mesh incubate</code></strong></p>
<p>This Mesh Developer Tools command allows you to create a component, whic=
h can be deployed to the incubator environment.</p>
</div>
</div>
<h4 id=3D"DeveloperInductionQuestions-Question3">Question 3</h4>
<p>What type of tests are run during Continuous Deployment?</p>
<ul>
<li>Unit tests</li>
<li>Idempotent tests</li>
<li>Load tests</li>
<li>User acceptance tests</li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<div id=3D"expander-1243644085" class=3D"expand-container">
<div role=3D"heading" aria-level=3D"6" id=3D"expander-control-1243644085" c=
lass=3D"expand-control"><button type=3D"button" id=3D"expand-button-1243644=
085" class=3D"aui-button aui-button-link aui-button-link-icon-text" aria-ex=
panded=3D"true" aria-controls=3D"expander-content-1243644085"><span class=
=3D"expand-icon aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-chevron-down" aria-hid=
den=3D"true"></span><span class=3D"expand-control-text conf-macro-render">C=
lick here to expand...</span></button>
</div>
<div role=3D"region" id=3D"expander-content-1243644085" class=3D"expand-con=
tent" aria-labelledby=3D"expand-button-1243644085">
<p><strong>Idempotent tests</strong></p>
<p>Tests defined in <code>idempotent_tests_postman_collection.json</code> a=
re executed during component deployment.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<h4 id=3D"DeveloperInductionQuestions-Question4">Question 4</h4>
<p>Which resource must always be implemented for your API to work in Westpa=
c Mesh?</p>
<ul>
<li>GET /healthcheck</li>
<li>GET /heartbeat</li>
<li>GET /status</li>
<li>GET /stats</li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<div id=3D"expander-1731887156" class=3D"expand-container">
<div role=3D"heading" aria-level=3D"6" id=3D"expander-control-1731887156" c=
lass=3D"expand-control"><button type=3D"button" id=3D"expand-button-1731887=
156" class=3D"aui-button aui-button-link aui-button-link-icon-text" aria-ex=
panded=3D"true" aria-controls=3D"expander-content-1731887156"><span class=
=3D"expand-icon aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-chevron-down" aria-hid=
den=3D"true"></span><span class=3D"expand-control-text conf-macro-render">C=
lick here to expand...</span></button>
</div>
<div role=3D"region" id=3D"expander-content-1731887156" class=3D"expand-con=
tent" aria-labelledby=3D"expand-button-1731887156">
<p><strong>GET /healthcheck</strong></p>
<p>This resource must be implemented and should return a HTTP 200 response.=
<br>
 The Mesh platform will poll /healthcheck to determine if your component is=
 running.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<h4 id=3D"DeveloperInductionQuestions-Question5">Question 5</h4>
<p>Your build has failed during Continuous Integration. What should you do =
first to find the root cause?</p>
<ul>
<li>Run '<code>mesh status</code>' in Developer Tools</li>
<li>Check Splunk dashboards</li>
<li>Check Bamboo logs</li>
<li>Contact Mesh service desk</li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<div id=3D"expander-1794798949" class=3D"expand-container">
<div role=3D"heading" aria-level=3D"6" id=3D"expander-control-1794798949" c=
lass=3D"expand-control"><button type=3D"button" id=3D"expand-button-1794798=
949" class=3D"aui-button aui-button-link aui-button-link-icon-text" aria-ex=
panded=3D"true" aria-controls=3D"expander-content-1794798949"><span class=
=3D"expand-icon aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-chevron-down" aria-hid=
den=3D"true"></span><span class=3D"expand-control-text conf-macro-render">C=
lick here to expand...</span></button>
</div>
<div role=3D"region" id=3D"expander-content-1794798949" class=3D"expand-con=
tent" aria-labelledby=3D"expand-button-1794798949">
<p><strong>Check Bamboo logs</strong></p>
<p>It is the developer's responsibility to perform basic troubleshooting fo=
r their own components.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<h4 id=3D"DeveloperInductionQuestions-Question6">Question 6</h4>
<p>Which of these commands can be used to encrypt sensitive information for=
 your components?</p>
<ul>
<li><code>mesh encrypt</code></li>
<li><code>mesh passwords</code></li>
<li><code>mesh secrets</code></li>
<li><code>mesh vault</code></li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<div id=3D"expander-1720405073" class=3D"expand-container">
<div role=3D"heading" aria-level=3D"6" id=3D"expander-control-1720405073" c=
lass=3D"expand-control"><button type=3D"button" id=3D"expand-button-1720405=
073" class=3D"aui-button aui-button-link aui-button-link-icon-text" aria-ex=
panded=3D"true" aria-controls=3D"expander-content-1720405073"><span class=
=3D"expand-icon aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-chevron-down" aria-hid=
den=3D"true"></span><span class=3D"expand-control-text conf-macro-render">C=
lick here to expand...</span></button>
</div>
<div role=3D"region" id=3D"expander-content-1720405073" class=3D"expand-con=
tent" aria-labelledby=3D"expand-button-1720405073">
<p><code><strong>mesh secrets</strong></code></p>
<p>This command will encrypt any files in your /secrets folder.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<h4 id=3D"DeveloperInductionQuestions-Question7">Question 7</h4>
<p>Which of these commands is NOT valid for deploying a component</p>
<ul>
<li><code>mesh deploy --component_name my-api-v1 --environment dev1</code><=
/li>
<li><code>mesh deploy --build_number 10 --environment dev1</code></li>
<li><code>mesh deploy --component_name my-api-v1 --build_number 10 --config=
_version 12 --environment dev1</code></li>
<li><code>mesh deploy --component_name my-api-v1 --build_number 10 --target=
 sit1</code></li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<div id=3D"expander-133201714" class=3D"expand-container">
<div role=3D"heading" aria-level=3D"6" id=3D"expander-control-133201714" cl=
ass=3D"expand-control"><button type=3D"button" id=3D"expand-button-13320171=
4" class=3D"aui-button aui-button-link aui-button-link-icon-text" aria-expa=
nded=3D"true" aria-controls=3D"expander-content-133201714"><span class=3D"e=
xpand-icon aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-chevron-down" aria-hidden=
=3D"true"></span><span class=3D"expand-control-text conf-macro-render">Clic=
k here to expand...</span></button>
</div>
<div role=3D"region" id=3D"expander-content-133201714" class=3D"expand-cont=
ent" aria-labelledby=3D"expand-button-133201714">
<p><strong><code>mesh deploy --component_name my-api-v1 --environment dev1<=
/code></strong></p>
<p>The build number must be specified.&nbsp;<br>
 Component name is optional, defaulting to the component in the current dir=
ectory.<br>
 Either target or environment must be specified.<br>
 Configuration and secret versions are optional, defaulting to the build nu=
mber.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<h4 id=3D"DeveloperInductionQuestions-Question8">Question 8</h4>
<p>Which of the following is TRUE about building a feature branch?</p>
<ul>
<li>The feature branch must be merged to the master branch before it can be=
 built</li>
<li>The feature branch must be enrolled in a swimlane before it can be buil=
t</li>
<li>The feature branch must checked out in the current directory before it =
can be built</li>
<li>The feature branch can be built, even when the component is not checked=
 out</li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<div id=3D"expander-1000685168" class=3D"expand-container">
<div role=3D"heading" aria-level=3D"6" id=3D"expander-control-1000685168" c=
lass=3D"expand-control"><button type=3D"button" id=3D"expand-button-1000685=
168" class=3D"aui-button aui-button-link aui-button-link-icon-text" aria-ex=
panded=3D"true" aria-controls=3D"expander-content-1000685168"><span class=
=3D"expand-icon aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-chevron-down" aria-hid=
den=3D"true"></span><span class=3D"expand-control-text conf-macro-render">C=
lick here to expand...</span></button>
</div>
<div role=3D"region" id=3D"expander-content-1000685168" class=3D"expand-con=
tent" aria-labelledby=3D"expand-button-1000685168">
<p><strong>The feature branch can be built, even when the component is not =
checked out</strong></p>
<p>Developers can run '<code>mesh build --component_name my-api-v1 --revisi=
on feature/example'</code> to build a feature branch of a component</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<h4 id=3D"DeveloperInductionQuestions-Question9">Question 9&nbsp;</h4>
<p>In addition to raising a consumption grant through Mesh Connect to consu=
me another component, which file must you update in your consuming componen=
t?</p>
<ul>
<li>component.yaml</li>
<li>consumptions.yaml</li>
<li>dependencies.yaml</li>
<li>resources.yaml</li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<div id=3D"expander-818485545" class=3D"expand-container">
<div role=3D"heading" aria-level=3D"6" id=3D"expander-control-818485545" cl=
ass=3D"expand-control"><button type=3D"button" id=3D"expand-button-81848554=
5" class=3D"aui-button aui-button-link aui-button-link-icon-text" aria-expa=
nded=3D"true" aria-controls=3D"expander-content-818485545"><span class=3D"e=
xpand-icon aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-chevron-down" aria-hidden=
=3D"true"></span><span class=3D"expand-control-text conf-macro-render">Clic=
k here to expand...</span></button>
</div>
<div role=3D"region" id=3D"expander-content-818485545" class=3D"expand-cont=
ent" aria-labelledby=3D"expand-button-818485545">
<p><strong>dependencies.yaml</strong></p>
<p>You should add the provider component to dependencies.yaml in your consu=
ming component.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<h4 id=3D"DeveloperInductionQuestions-Question10">Question 10</h4>
<p>Which of the follow is FALSE about Virtual Swimlanes in the Mesh?</p>
<ul>
<li>Mesh Developer Tools can be used to enrol a new swimlane</li>
<li>All dependencies must be enrolled in the same swimlane</li>
<li>Multiple swimlanes are allowed for any one environment</li>
<li>Dependencies can use the swimlane without requiring code changes</li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<div id=3D"expander-524782543" class=3D"expand-container">
<div role=3D"heading" aria-level=3D"6" id=3D"expander-control-524782543" cl=
ass=3D"expand-control"><button type=3D"button" id=3D"expand-button-52478254=
3" class=3D"aui-button aui-button-link aui-button-link-icon-text" aria-expa=
nded=3D"true" aria-controls=3D"expander-content-524782543"><span class=3D"e=
xpand-icon aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-chevron-down" aria-hidden=
=3D"true"></span><span class=3D"expand-control-text conf-macro-render">Clic=
k here to expand...</span></button>
</div>
<div role=3D"region" id=3D"expander-content-524782543" class=3D"expand-cont=
ent" aria-labelledby=3D"expand-button-524782543">
<p><strong>All dependencies must be enrolled in the same swimlane</strong><=
/p>
<p>If a dependency is not enrolled in the same swimlane as the consuming co=
mponent, then the request is routed to dependency deployed in the default s=
wimlane.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<p><br></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
